Description
------------
This program is a small simulator of the movement of celestial objects in 2 dimensions. It was realized in C++ with 
the help of the QT framework. 

For help please click the about button. 

Version
-------
1.0 : First release


Future improvements 
-------------------

 - improve the drawing of the planets
 - allow to change the properties of a planet before creation
 - use of the mouse roller to change the mass of planets